## Run with Docker

Build the image:

```bash
docker build -t document-intake-app .
```

Run the container (frontend on port 8080, backend on 8000):

```bash
docker run --rm -p 8080:80 -p 8000:8000 document-intake-app
```

Then open:
- Frontend: http://localhost:8080
- Backend: http://localhost:8000/docs
